igh school student on the varsity baseball team. His mother hired me to create a website where he could showcase his history, statistics, and&nbsp;achievements to college recruiters.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"37\":[\"86\",\"78\",\"75\",\"58\",\"59\",\"57\"],\"19\":{\"date\":\"6\\/1\\/2013\"},\"32\":\"\",\"17\":\"dakotasolomon.com\",\"18\":\"http:\\/\\/\"}}', '2016-10-03 20:32:40', '2016-10-03 20:32:40', 'b73238e8-1435-48d2-9f49-fe7689f120c6'),
 ('215', '92', '4', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Brooke Fletcher\",\"slug\":\"brooke-fletcher\",\"postDate\":1475543951,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Brooke was a trained photographer who had turned her professional attention to web development and user experience. Her web development experience was primarily focused on enterprise content management systems that were too cumbersome and expensive for a personal portfolio site. Brooke sought my advice and assistance with setting up a Wordpress site.<\\/p><p>I helped Brooke by guiding her through the setup process, plugins, themes. ,etc.<\\/p>\",\"20\":{\"date\":\"8\\/1\\/14\"},\"15\":\"1\",\"12\":\"\",\"11\":\"\",\"21\":\"<p>Brooke was a UX&nbsp;generalist with development experience using enterprise content management systems. I consulted with Brooke on using Wordpress to build her personal portfolio website.<\\/p>\",\"37\":[\"78\",\"75\",\"59\"],\"19\":{\"date\":\"7\\/1\\/14\"},\"32\":\"\",\"17\":\"brookefletcher.com\",\"18\":\"http:\\/\\/\"}}', '2016-10-04 01:19:11', '2016-10-04 01:19:11', '06b05e9d-d28e-456f-b365-fc9d0065c7c8'),
